ABOUT
=====
Convert ppt document to pdf document using JODconverter and OpenOffice

REQUIREMENTS
============
* OpenOffice v2.0.3 or higher
* Java
* Bash

USAGE
=====
Usage: ppt2pdf.sh [options] [filename]
    options: -r: Recursive,
    	     -a: All file in this directory,
    	     -y: Answare YES to all question,
	     -v: Verbose (if not use default is 1),
	     -h: Usage.
    verbose: 0 no output,
	     1 a little bit of info,
	     2 a lot of info.

